OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773774690
OL,3,CEnvironment Agency to invest millions
OL,4,Cinto flood defences
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency is investing
OL,7,Fmillions of pounds into flood
OL,8,Fmanagement across the North West.
OL,10,FIt is part of a #1.4 billion
OL,11,Finvestment in flood defences to help
OL,12,Fprotect homes and businesses across
OL,13,FEngland, in what is being described as
OL,14,Fthe largest flood defence programme in
OL,15,Fthe country's history.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
