PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773774690
OL,3,CEnvironment Agency to invest millions
OL,4,Cinto flood defences
OL,6,FAround 5000 homes in Lancashire will
OL,7,Fbenefit from the #15.2 million being
OL,8,Fspent on defences in Preston and South
OL,9,FRibble. Money is also being spent on
OL,10,Fflood management around Blackpool
OL,11,FBeach.
OL,13,FThe programme also includes a #300
OL,14,Fmillion investment in natural flood
OL,15,Fmanagement across England over the
OL,16,Fnext decade.
OL,18,FThis approach uses measures such as
OL,19,Ftree planting, restoring rivers and
OL,20,Fcreating wetlands to slow water flow
OL,21,Fand reduce flood risk.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
