FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773774690
OL,3,CEnvironment Agency to invest millions
OL,4,Cinto flood defences
OL,6,FOne example is work led by the Ribble
OL,7,FRivers Trust, which is installing
OL,8,F"leaky barriers" and restoring
OL,9,Ffloodplains near Clitheroe to help
OL,10,Freduce flooding while improving local
OL,11,Fecosystems.
OL,13,FThe work is aimed at reducing the
OL,14,Fimpact of flooding on communities and
OL,15,Finfrastructure.
OL,17,FAn additional #260 million will be
OL,18,Fused to repair and maintain existing
OL,19,Fflood defences, including those
OL,20,Fdamaged during Storms Goretti and
OL,21,FChandra.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
