CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773774690
OL,3,CEnvironment Agency to invest millions
OL,4,Cinto flood defences
OL,6,FOfficials say the funding will help
OL,7,Freverse a long-term decline in the
OL,8,Fcondition of flood assets.
OL,10,FAccording to Government estimates,
OL,11,Fevery #1 invested in flood defences
OL,12,Fprevents around #8 in economic damage,
OL,13,Fmeaning the latest investment could
OL,14,Fhelp avoid more than #10 billion in
OL,15,Flosses.
OL,17,FFloods Minister Emma Hardy said the
OL,18,Ffunding would strengthen protections
OL,19,Ffor families and businesses while also
OL,20,Fsupporting job creation and economic
OL,21,Fgrowth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
