PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773774690
OL,3,CEnvironment Agency to invest millions
OL,4,Cinto flood defences
OL,6,FMs Hardy said: "Flooding can turn
OL,7,Flives upside down in a matter of
OL,8,Fhours, destroying homes, shutting down
OL,9,Fbusinesses and leaving communities
OL,10,Ffacing months of heartbreak and
OL,11,Frecovery.
OL,13,F"This #1.4 billion investment will
OL,14,Fhelp protect tens of thousands of
OL,15,Fhomes and businesses across the
OL,16,Fcountry and strengthen the defences
OL,17,Ffamilies rely on when the worst
OL,18,Fhappens.
OL,26,@nD@POUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
