OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773774690
OL,3,CEnvironment Agency to invest millions
OL,4,Cinto flood defences
OL,6,F"We've already stepped in to stabilise
OL,7,Four flood assets after years of
OL,8,Fdecline and this funding goes further,
OL,9,Fcreating thousands of jobs, protecting
OL,10,Fcommunities from billions of pounds of
OL,11,Fdamage, and unlocking new homes and
OL,12,Fbusinesses in places made safer from
OL,13,Fflooding."
OL,15,FCaroline Douglass, Environment Agency
OL,16,FExecutive Director for Flood and
OL,17,FCoastal Risk Management, said: "In
OL,18,Fpartnership with local authorities,
OL,19,Fhomes and businesses will benefit from
OL,20,Fstronger defences with more than 600
OL,21,Fschemes being delivered across England.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@JO]yD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
