OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773774690
OL,3,CEnvironment Agency to invest millions
OL,4,Cinto flood defences
OL,6,F"From major flood barriers and
OL,7,Fstrengthened embankments to natural
OL,8,Fflood management and coastal defence
OL,9,Fprojects, we're combining engineering
OL,10,Fand nature-based solutions to reduce
OL,11,Fflood risk and build long-term
OL,12,Fresilience for communities across the
OL,13,Fcountry."
OL,15,FOfficials say the overall programme is
OL,16,Fdesigned to strengthen the country's
OL,17,Fresilience to increasingly frequent
OL,18,Fextreme weather, while protecting
OL,19,Fcommunities, supporting jobs and
OL,20,Fenabling future development in areas
OL,21,Fat risk of flooding.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]
